      "id": "mem_mr3h9ccf_p7hos6mq",
      "content": "This project was renamed (clean break, 2026-06) from `ruflo` / `claude-flow` to **`rufflo`**. Apply consistently:\n\n- **Repo / git remote:** `git@github.com:JannieP/rufflo.git` (origin). NOT ruvnet/ruflo.\n- **Canonical npm package:** `rufflo` (the repo-root package). The old `ruflo/` wrapper was retired to name `rufflo-bridge` + `private: true` to resolve the collision.\n- **npm scope:** `@rufflo/*` (e.g. `@rufflo/cli`). Source dirs moved `v3/@claude-flow/` → `v3/@rufflo/`.\n- **CLI binary / commands:** `rufflo` (e.g. `npx -y rufflo mcp start`). Storage dir `.claude-flow/` → `.rufflo/` (one-time auto-migration on first run lives in `v3/@rufflo/cli/src/storage-migration.ts`).\n- **Preserved deliberately (do NOT rewrite):** upstream attribution URLs `github.com/ruvnet/claude-flow` and `ruvnet/ruflo`, and env vars (`CLAUDE_FLOW_*`, `RUFLO_*` — left as-is to avoid breaking existing shells).\n\nSee [[commit-push-in-phases]] for the working style on this repo.",
